    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Hyper Rush</strong></i> is a <i>single-player, leaderboard-based</i>, <i>competitive speed-racing game</i> where you battle to become the top <i>Baller</i> in <i>Rush City</i>. Launch your <i>Orball</i> into the <i>Holodrome</i>, competing in freeform platforming tracks to set the best times, and earn enough medals to work your way though the leagues...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Omnidirectional movement means you'll use your <i>Orball's</i> <i>drifting, wall riding, jumping</i>, <i>boosting, </i>and <i>nudging </i>abilities to find creative ways to be the fastest though each track, against your friends, and the world.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/8cda7301d2df7d5fa117a1bf1239116b.poster.avif?t=1770275775\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/8cda7301d2df7d5fa117a1bf1239116b.webm?t=1770275775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/8cda7301d2df7d5fa117a1bf1239116b.mp4?t=1770275775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abilities mix up how you approach each track, like Annie-Mae's Javelin to grapple across ledges. Make clever use of them to  find paths to the end goal that were otherwise impossible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/1dcccb40f56e943740c8164d6fb421ff.poster.avif?t=1770275775\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/1dcccb40f56e943740c8164d6fb421ff.webm?t=1770275775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/1dcccb40f56e943740c8164d6fb421ff.mp4?t=1770275775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with other players as you race against their ghosts: see how you fare against the competition and learn from the paths they take. Secure the top spots to increase your HYPER RANK.   <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/250dbb399a3d5c347543904e94d499b1.poster.avif?t=1770275775\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/250dbb399a3d5c347543904e94d499b1.webm?t=1770275775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/250dbb399a3d5c347543904e94d499b1.mp4?t=1770275775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize your times across dozens of multi-layered, multi-pathed, replayable tracks, while earning medals to unlock new leagues, Ballers, and abilities. Watch replays of leaderboard champions to learn their strats. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/c152429fd1b7feb39cc44f675e820d4c.poster.avif?t=1770275775\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/c152429fd1b7feb39cc44f675e820d4c.webm?t=1770275775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1831460/extras/c152429fd1b7feb39cc44f675e820d4c.mp4?t=1770275775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
